{"type":"message","id":"242921c0","parentId":"d0e99356","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:03:53.273Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sqyu85527kl4_1","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 3,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774627429532,\n      \"sessionId\": \"fa03df49-fc5c-49cd-9b99-60234caa771f\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 43321,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/fa03df49-fc5c-49cd-9b99-60234caa771f.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"The subagent completed a research task on industry trends related to 道简网络's business. The results have been saved to a memory file. This is useful information that should be shared with 姚总 for his business decision-making.\\n\\nLet me check if this is something that needs to be surfaced to the user (姚总), or if it's just an internal orchestration update.\\n\\nLooking at the task - it was to search for industry trends and save to a file. The subagent completed it successfully. The results are summarized. \\n\\nThis seems like a research/learning task that was delegated. The findings are substantive (5 industry areas, ~25+ key information points). This could be valuable for 姚总 to see, especially since the SOUL.md emphasizes proactive learning and staying current on industry trends.\\n\\nI should surface a concise summary to 姚总 rather than just marking it as done internally.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"<final>\\n🦞 子Agent已完成行业动态调研，结果已保存到 `memory/学习笔记.md`。\\n\\n**核心发现摘要：**\\n\\n| 领域 | 关键趋势 |\\n|------|---------|\\n| **企业数字化转型** | 数据要素市场化加速；AI+制造业规模化落地；中小企业获专项扶持 |\\n| **智能安防/智慧城市** | 云边端协同架构成为主流；AI行为识别普及；城市综合治理深化 |\\n| **网络系统集成** | 市场规模1.8-2.1万亿；自智网络L4加速落地；国产化替代机遇显现 |\\n| **IT运维服务** | AIOps智能体故障自愈率73%；\\\"主动预判\\\"替代\\\"被动响应\\\"；渗透率40%并加速 |\\n| **To B科技服务** | AI Agent驱动服务模式变革；按效果付费RaaS新模式兴起；哑铃型市场结构 |\\n\\n**道简关联机会**：网络集成+智能安防+IT运维三大业务线均处于政策红利期，AI与自动化的深度融合是今年最大变量。\\n\\n如需查阅完整内容或基于某一领域深入分析，请告诉我。\\n</final>\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774627197505\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:99dd3c6e-f440-4ce5-a3aa-579918ee141b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774627290840,\n      \"sessionId\": \"29a4763b-c2e2-4a0d-a7bf-23d514821d97\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 45028,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/29a4763b-c2e2-4a0d-a7bf-23d514821d97.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"aborted\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774627298472,\n          \"errorMessage\": \"Request was aborted.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:a44cea8b-b0c2-417d-8c31-744a5e681e